snippet.title: Andes Attack for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Andes Attack is a clone of Defender.

Aliens want to kidnap the llamas that live in the Andes. It is your task to destroy those aliens and save the llamas!
